OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FA teenager has described how a serious
OL,8,Fhead injury sustained while on a
OL,9,Ffootball holiday in Ibiza left him on
OL,10,Fa stroke ward for four months.
OL,12,FDaniel Hurst went on an annual
OL,13,Ffootball trip to the popular holiday
OL,14,Fdestination in May last year with his
OL,15,Fteammates from Yateley United Football
OL,16,FClub.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FBut the trip ended in catastrophe
OL,8,Fafter Mr Hurst, who was 19 at the
OL,9,Ftime, suffered such a horrific head
OL,10,Finjury that medics did not believe he
OL,11,Fwould survive.
OL,13,FAfter going on an evening out with
OL,14,Fclub members, including his father
OL,15,FSteve, Mr Hurst decided to head 300
OL,16,Fyards back to the hotel.
OL,18,FBut he disappeared and teammates set
OL,19,Fout to look for him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FSeveral hours later, his father was
OL,8,Ftold by police that a British boy had
OL,9,Fbeen taken to hospital with severe
OL,10,Fhead injuries and was not expected to
OL,11,Fmake it through the night.
OL,13,FMr Hurst was airlifted to Majorca and
OL,14,Fneeded surgery which involved medics
OL,15,Fremoving part of his skull to try to
OL,16,Fstop the swelling.
OL,18,FHe was put in a medically induced coma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FAfter four weeks in hospital on the
OL,8,FSpanish island he was stable enough to
OL,9,Fbe airlifted to Frimley Park Hospital
OL,10,Fin Surrey where he spent four months
OL,11,Fon a stroke unit in a bed for patients
OL,12,Fwho suffer traumatic brain injuries.
OL,14,FHe was the youngest ever patient to be
OL,15,Fcared for on Frimley's stroke ward.
OL,17,FWhen he arrived at the hospital he was
OL,18,Funable to walk or talk but thanks to
OL,19,Fthe care he received he is now
OL,20,Fplanning to run the London Marathon to
OL,21,Fraise money for the hospital's charity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FMr Hurst, who works at a local golf
OL,8,Fclub, is also back playing some
OL,9,Ffootball with his teammates.
OL,11,FHe also wants to raise awareness that
OL,12,F"recovery is possible" after such a
OL,13,Ftraumatic injury.
OL,15,F"You have to keep moving forward," he
OL,16,Ftold the Press Association.
OL,18,F"I've got the same plans now I did
OL,19,Fbefore it happened ` I'm trying to
OL,20,Fimprove my golf, I'm running a lot, I
OL,21,Fgo to the gym, things like that.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@VO]wD@AOUwD@bO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,F"It's obviously been pushed back a
OL,8,Flittle bit, but not a lot.
OL,10,F"I want to help motivate people (with
OL,11,Fbrain injuries) to just keep going
OL,12,Fforward ` your life is never over.
OL,14,F"I know it is hard. There were moments
OL,15,Fwhen I thought 'is my life done?'...
OL,16,Fbut you have got to keep going."
OL,18,FMr Hurst praised the hospital staff at
OL,19,FFrimley Park Hospital, saying that
OL,20,Fthey have kept him motivated.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FOn the marathon, he added: "Even if I
OL,8,Fjust walk it, this year is not about
OL,9,Fbeating my time last year, it is about
OL,10,Fgetting over the finish line."
OL,12,FIn a message to holiday-goers, he
OL,13,Fsaid: "I would urge people to just be
OL,14,Fcareful and always stick with at least
OL,15,Fone or two people, just always stay
OL,16,Ftogether."
OL,18,FHis father Steve, 53, added: "The
OL,19,Fmessage is just, 'stick with someone,
OL,20,Fjust be wary of surroundings', like
OL,21,FDan said. This could happen anywhere."
OL,26,@oD@\OUrD@^O]uD@GOUxD@JO]zD@^OU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
