PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,FOn the incident, he said: "We couldn't
OL,8,Ffind Dan, I rang his phone and police
OL,9,Fanswered.
OL,11,F"They said someone who fits Dan's
OL,12,Fdescription had been admitted to
OL,13,Fhospital.
OL,15,F"We were told there was a very high
OL,16,Fchance that he wouldn't make it ` they
OL,17,Fwere quite blunt about the severity of
OL,18,Fhis injuries.
OL,20,F"I had to ring his mum and tell her
OL,21,Fwhat happened, it was horrendous.
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@AOUwD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,F"Even after his surgery in Majorca we
OL,8,Fwere told that it was an 'hour-by-
OL,9,Fhour, day-by-day' situation."
OL,11,FDr Tilly Speirs, consultant stroke
OL,12,Fphysician at Frimley Health NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust, one of Mr Hurst's
OL,14,Fmedics, told the Press Association:
OL,15,F"When he arrived we had to start right
OL,16,Ffrom the beginning and work out what
OL,17,Fhis deficits were and what therapy he
OL,18,Fwas going to need.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@]O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,F"He couldn't walk when he came to us
OL,8,Fand it was a really scary time for his
OL,9,Ffamily because they didn't know what
OL,10,Fwas going to happen and whether he
OL,11,Fwould recover.
OL,13,F"He had post-traumatic amnesia when he
OL,14,Farrived... he couldn't recall what
OL,15,Fhappened the day before or the hour
OL,16,Fbefore.
OL,18,F"He survived the head injury but the
OL,19,Ffamily didn't know what that survival
OL,20,Fwas going to look like.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,F"As a team we didn't know either but
OL,8,Fwe knew he needed to have rehab and
OL,9,Fhe's done remarkably well.
OL,11,F"He had age on his side, he had just
OL,12,Frun a marathon so he was in good
OL,13,Fphysical condition before this
OL,14,Fhappened.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773806609
OL,3,CTeenager tells of spending months on
OL,4,Cstroke ward after horror incident in
OL,5,CIbiza
OL,7,F"Dan is a testament that with rehab
OL,8,Fthat you can have a good outcome
OL,9,Ffollowing a traumatic brain injury,
OL,10,Fit's not going to be the same for
OL,11,Feverybody, it really depends on the
OL,12,Findividual, but he has done remarkably
OL,13,Fwell and I think his future is going
OL,14,Fto be as bright as it was before he
OL,15,Fwent on that trip."
OL,17,F` The London Marathon is taking place
OL,18,Fon Sunday April 26 and Mr Hurst has
OL,19,Fset up a fundraising page at
OL,20,Fjustgiving.com/page/danhurst20.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
